FogBugz
========

payload
-------
  refer to docs/github_payload

data
----
  - cvssubmit_url (The url to the cvsSubmit.[php|asp] file on your FogBugz server. Example: https://server.com/fogbugz/cvsSubmit.php)
  
  
notes
-----
Be sure to set up your FogBugz installation to handle multiple repositories/multiple source control systems as described in http://www.fogcreek.com/FogBugz/KB/howto/MultipleRepositories-Mult.html

The "sRepo" field will be set to the name of the github repo.

